_sText:
This was a reinvention of fy_ducksoup_beta.

To prevent excessive camping, the sewers become inaccessable 1/2 way through the map, and then the oil towers explode at about 2:20, killing anyone who is camping and avoiding combat.

The cover pieces the players initially start behind are destructable.

The sewer is especially dark and NV works well down there.  There is also a buyzone down there.
